publisher			DreamsSoftGames							
publish_time	 2015年5月22日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							"Tompi Jones" is a fun old style platform game in 2.5D where you will help Tompi across six worlds: the Aztec Pyramid, the Enchanted Forest, the Kingdom of Arkan, the Mysterious Jungle, the Dark Cemetery and the Fortress of Edom.Tompi can walk, jump, roll on the ground, he can plan with the propeller he has in his hat, throw many types of projectile weapons, defend himself with a shield, fight with a sword, use a jetpack, climb the lianas, cling to ceilings, climb walls and jump between walls.He can also use special items as stop the time, become invisible, super speed, enhance his projectile weapons or use the invulnerability.Collect all the secret pieces and coins scattered throughout the levels to improve your skills, and to buy and improve your weapons and special items.The game has an Online World Ranking. If you get enough coins you will be in the top 50!.						
title	 Tompi Jones			
